import React from 'react';
import './ProfileCard.css';
import {
  Card,
  CardHeader,
  CardContent,
  Grid,
  Avatar,
  Typography,
} from '@material-ui/core';
import Rating from '@mui/material/Rating';
export default function ProfileCard({ data }) {
  return (
    <Card className="custom-card">
      <CardHeader title={data.title} className="custom-card-header" />
      <CardContent className="custom-card-content">
        <Grid container spacing={2}>
          <Grid item xs={3}  className="avatar-column">
            <Avatar className="avatar" src={data.profileImage} alt="User Avatar" />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={3}  className="avatar-column">
          <Typography variant="body1" font="bold" className="name" component="h1">
                  Rs 900
                </Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={9}>
            <Grid container spacing={1}>
              <Grid item xs={12}>
                <Typography variant="body1" font="bold" className="name" component="h1">
                  Rs 900
                </Typography>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={12}>
                <Rating name="read-only" value={data.rating} precision={0.1} readOnly />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={12}>
                <Rating name="read-only" value={data.rating} precision={0.1} readOnly />
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
  );
}
